### ─────────────────────────────
### MENU TYPES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar tipos de menú (STAFF)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener tipo de menú por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu-types/{{menuTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear tipo de menú (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/menu-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Menú Vegano"
}

###

### Actualizar tipo de menú (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/menu-types/{{menuTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Vegetariano",
  "sort_order": 3,
  "active": true
}

###

### Eliminar tipo de menú (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/menu-types/{{menuTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
